埃洛伊·卡萨格兰德（Eloy Casagrande）解释了离开塞普尔图拉（Sepultura https://www.nme.com/news/music/eloy-casagrande-explains-complecated-decision-to-to-leave-sepultura-sepultura-for-slipknot-3755878？决策 -  sepultura for-slipknotEmma Wilkes Mon, 13 May 2024 20:45:01 +0000 Music NewsNewsMetal https://www.nme.com/?p=3755878 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/eloy-casagrande-mauro-pimentel-2.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="埃洛伊·卡萨格兰德" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/eloy-casagrande-mauro-pimentel-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/eloy-casagrande-mauro-pimentel-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/eloy-casagrande-mauro-pimentel-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/eloy-casagrande-mauro-pimentel-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/eloy-casagrande-mauro-pimentel-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/eloy-casagrande-mauro-pimentel-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “乐队要分手了，我不想在33岁时停止打鼓”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/eloy-casagrande-explains-complicated-decision-to-leave-sepultura-for-slipknot-3755878">埃洛伊·卡萨格兰德（Eloy Casagrande）邮报解释了“复杂”离开塞普尔图拉（Sepultura）进行Slipknot的决定，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/eloy-casagrande-mauro-pimentel-2.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="埃洛伊·卡萨格兰德" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/eloy-casagrande-mauro-pimentel-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/eloy-casagrande-mauro-pimentel-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/eloy-casagrande-mauro-pimentel-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/eloy-casagrande-mauro-pimentel-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/eloy-casagrande-mauro-pimentel-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/eloy-casagrande-mauro-pimentel-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>埃洛伊·卡萨格兰德（Eloy Casagrande）公开了他离开<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sepultura">塞普尔图拉（Sepultura）</a>填补<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/slipknot">Slipknot</a>中空缺的鼓手位置的原因。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-clown-interview-tour-2024-tickets-new-material-3559353"><b>Slipknot的小丑演讲2024 Tour和新材料：“这支乐队从未更快乐”</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>卡萨格兰德（Casagrande）于2月 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sepultura-drummer-quits-band-ahead-of-final-tour-3594013">离开了巴西金属乐队</a>，他将在今年开始的告别巡回演出后分手。这导致人们强烈猜测他将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-announce-departure-of-drummer-jay-weinberg-3531261">在去年年底杰伊·温伯格（Jay Weinberg）开除</a>后加入Slipknot。</p><p>卡萨格兰德（Casagrande）最近接受了巴西的<a href="https://vejasp.abril.com.br/coluna/tudo-de-som/eloy-casagrande-slipknot-entrevista/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Veja Sao Paulo</a>的采访， <a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/Slipknot/comments/1copad0/eng_translation_eloy_casagrande_interview_with/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Reddit上的粉丝</a>从他的祖国葡萄牙语中翻译出来。</p><p>他透露，他问他在两个乐队中演奏，但在被告知他必须独有的slipknot之后，不得不离开塞普尔图拉。</p><p>他说：“他们要求我录制并向他们发送一些来自巴西的视频。” “最初有三首歌曲，然后他们要求我再三首歌曲，问我是否有任何计划去美国的计划，我计划在一月份在我的乐器音乐项目Casagrande＆Hanysz那里演出。所以他们把我的航班时间提前了一点，我在棕榈泉呆了五天，和整个乐队一起排练。</p><p>他继续说：“然后他们要求我再延长五天的时间，以便我们记录一些事情。” “我认为这也是试镜的一部分。他们向我提出了新的想法，看看我的歌曲创作是什么样的。他们想从各方面考验我。”</p><p>直到2月初，Slip Knot才决定了Casagrande是否进行了裁员。</p><p>他说：“ Slipknot由九位音乐家组成，因此有很多领域和层次，他们需要在给我还可以的每个人之前得到认可。”</p><p>正式的邀请是在塞普尔图拉（Sepultura）宣布将分裂的情况下，卡萨格兰德（Casagrande）解释说，这对他试镜了，这是一个很大的吸引力。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C6a4elSumsi/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" da